msgstr "Geregistreerde gebruikers"

msgid "Are the registered users relatives or relatives by marriage?"
msgstr "Zijn de geregistreerde gebruikers familieleden of aangetrouwde familieleden?"

msgid "Select this only if registered users are limited to relatives or relatives by marriage and family-internal confidentiality should be stated in the privacy policy."
msgstr ""
